I have a branch I have not opened PR yet.
I just want to make sure this fashion will be satisfying.
My current implementation directly utilizes `ExternOp`:
attr map stores all the elements in the argument list;
body is the parsed function body;
input tensors are those tensors read by operations in the body;
input buffers are those buffers of the corresponding tensors;
output buffers are the buffers of the output tensor wrote by the operations in the body;
